values:
Dear all of you,

I will not be writing in this journal any longer. I've decided to start a new life and a new journal. If I want to remain your friend I have already contacted you or added you to my friend's list, if not...oh well.

-Allee

The heart, not just the organ that pumps blood, seperates unoxygenated and oxygenated blood, and sends blood throughout the entire body via the aorta and vena cava ;). But when drawn, it can take on new meanings. After I typed all the examples up, I realized none of them made sense. From the incredibly strange examples, and state of mind I'm in would have given people another reason to think I'm on drugs, or currently at the bottom of a bottle. So I'll leave you with.. Love sucks.

Time doesn't stop for those who dream...

...I wake only to hear this scream..

Well, don't fall for crushes, tis not worth it. Don't cry over spilt milk either. 

Enjoy art, sometimes it's the only escape...

On vacation until June 20... Yay..going to be a pirate in the caribbean.

Anyone going anywhere?
Today is just an ordinary wedensday, besides the fact there's a math final today and it's going to rain.
Only time when the mall isn't boring is when hanging out with John, Mike, Amy and Nikki.. that is all =)
Okay, so apparently my new name is Shmee... sure... don't let random people on your computer kids.
Lord of the Rings just got better.
Singing and dancing in the rain, today. Thunderstorms too, whee!
Wake me up, from this bad dream..
That's pretty much how I feel lately.
Word of Advice to busy people: Don't play Drakengard... that is all..
Hey it's 4am, maybe I should get some sleep..Nah.
Being different is one thing, dressing unique is another, and acting disrespectful is another thing...
I am the queen of France..but I'm Canadain.. =)
Jobs sound good, well, only the money part. The rest of it sucks...

Today is a good day. Feeling good mentally and physically, being able to sleep at night without waking up not being able to breathe. It's a beautiful day, walks with realizing how perfect the world is with all it's type of people and incredible nature. Also realizing how great my friends really are, thank you all kindly for all your encouraging and kind words, Thank you

Just saw a Modest Mouse music video on mtv...Now what is that about?

Isaac singing about happy things with a new cleaned up act.. It's not right..
My family is breaking up...Just great..*sighs*..

Last night, was the worse night ever in this house... Some people think I overreact but.. the story is so horribly sad, I can't describe... it could take an entire 3 days to explain what happened..

Sickness and sinus inflections have filled this house as well as chaos.. and it's killing me.. literally..
Relationships are for people who don't have ADHD, and not enough problems in their life. =)
Life is just becoming sleep. Just nightmares and peaceful dreams, from one nightmare into another.

Life is boring lately, the same routine in and out, everyday. Hopefully something will spark some interest pretty soon. Trying to enjoy the days now, it's not horrible, it's just a bit  boring, then at the end of the day no time to do anything you want to do.  And that's what bothers me...you know?..That feeling of working incredibly hard and going nowhere? 

..I haven't been hanging around after school for Art on Tuesdays and Thursdays lately...Not sure why, it's a weird feeling theres a lot to do but not a lot to do, just want to get it done and have time to relax, and not constantly being pushed in every direction possible..I have to start again before everyone graduates.
Alright. This morning at 6:43. Huh? oh The weather is still beautiful in a student's mind.
Well Secret Window was interesting. The story writting was iffy, but the acting was incredible. Anyway cheerios don't taste good at 6:19am. eh..

Well today was Spirit Day...... and that's all I have to say about Spirit Day. My brother gave me his perfectly great stereo which sounds amazing...my brother and technology don't mix, so when he couldn't figure out how to use it, he gave it to me and bought a new one..

It feels like...it's colder than it ought to be in march. And I've still got a day or two ahead of me..and the people here are asking after you..it doesn't make it easier..it doesn't make it easier to be away..warmer where you're waiting..it feels more like july..

A wallet my sister had boughten me is lost...I'm REALLY upset.. I lost $30, IDs, cards, change, pictures, and more... I want to die because I lost it...I suck at being a human being..Why out of everything did I lose that??.. It was green and sort of new..Just dandy. *sighs*

Math is evil.. It's out to make people miserable!


Justin's lucky guitar pick is in my possession, heheheheh.


Anyone else have a heartache during the new Jesus movie? Come on..that's like going to see Titanic...Gee I wonder what happens at the end..
The show was incredible...theres another one on saturday. Three saturdays in a row...holy shit this rocks.
Thanks Snapple for sharing...I couldn't of felt like eating without you! The show is going to be great on Saturday.
Life is hetric. Meals are good, and shows are going pretty decent. Life is also tiring. All work, no sleep or play. Life is a lot better than it could be.
Hey, everyone should pretend it's a weekend and go back to sleep! Sounds like a dandy idea.. I think..

Vacation is over...life goes back to the "norm" tomorrow. As much as everyone says they never want to go back. I really mean it, I don't like my school at all, I'm failing miserably there. My parents are religious freaks, it's more important to make your child completely unhappy in a private school. Maybe I'm just being silly, wouldn't be the first.. =/

The now French cultured friends are back from their week in Paris, according to Cassie. Just a random thought: are there peanut butter and jelly sandwiches in France? I might add pictures depending on tongiht.
I listen to screamy and whiney yet harmonic and melodic sappy rock, and I fucking love it.

When the sun sets it's so beautiful how the sky turns pinkish and orangey colors, and just so amazing watching the sky prepare for the darkness to fall..

I'm starting to notice many other things around me. More emotions, colors, lighting, everything. I just wish everything would stop being so drawn out and dull. Summer is so close but so far... I just feel alone.. I guess..

Yeah..it's 3:13am...

The hell with love...

It's now 3:14am..

Damn the clock keeps ticking away...and away and away..

Sitting around Denny's for hours is the cure for early morning boredom.
Valentine's day is a commercial holiday.
What a Smooth Criminal, Rachel is.
...It's like 35 degrees outside, it's like fucking summer.
Hours fly, but days go by so very slowly.

Apparently there's a new system coming out for the tags sewn into clothes. The companies that make all the tags and sew them on, are putting this tiny microchip into the tags to assure nobody steals stuff. With this mircochip in the clothes tags the companies will be able to track their inventory from other companies, and track anywhere the person goes, if they had stole it. If the person had bought it, the cashier deactivates the device at the register...

That idea is scary as all fuck.. I found this pamphlet in a magazine one of my parents reads looking for something else, that talks about this new tag technology..

Somewhere A Seed Somewhere a seed falls to the ground That will become a tree That will some day be felled From which thin shafts will be extracted To be made into arrows To be fitted with warheads One of which, some day when you least expect it, While a winter sun is shining On a river of ice And you feel farthest from self-pity, Will pierce your shit-filled heart. ~Michael Fried
Today started so beautiful but then turned into shit quickly..Oh well, it happens..
